Dude, i'm having the EXACT same problem, weird thing is, i have had this game installed for over a year, played it many, many, many times with ZERO problems. I'm almost finished yet another play through, right at the last part when you have to take the shuttle to the next mission and just as you said, it gets stuck at the loading screen. I hear the ship sounds, the audio is still working, but nothing is loading... it's just stuck.

